are not negative.

1077
00:48:57,020 --> 00:48:59,900
It turns out that there's a very
deep philosophical connection

1078
00:48:59,900 --> 00:49:03,022
between finance and physics
that we're going to get to.

1079
00:49:03,022 --> 00:49:05,480
But this is something that you
don't need to be a physicist

1080
00:49:05,480 --> 00:49:06,270
to understand.

1081
00:49:06,270 --> 00:49:08,570
In fact, I'd argue
that Warren Buffett,

1082
00:49:08,570 --> 00:49:13,270
although he may not be able to
articulate these principles,

1083
00:49:13,270 --> 00:49:15,750
these are principles
