1086
00:49:22,410 --> 00:49:24,870
And he also knows that
$1 today without risk

1087
00:49:24,870 --> 00:49:27,810
is not the same as $1 today
with a little bit of risk.

1088
00:49:27,810 --> 00:49:31,440
Even a tiny little bit
